Section 3

This is going to make a plot! Generate a dataframe, then use ggplot to make a scatterplot.

# option + cmd + i
plot_df = 
  tibble(
    x = rnorm(n = 1000),
    y = 1 + 2 * x + rnorm(n = 1000)
  )

ggplot(plot_df, aes(x = x, y = y)) + geom_point()

la_df = 
  tibble(
    norm = rnorm(n = 500, mean = 1),
    logical = norm > 0,
    abs_norm = abs(norm)
  )

ggplot(la_df, aes(x = abs_norm)) + geom_histogram()
